                &lt;h2&gt;What's New in 0.0.21&lt;/h2&gt;
                &lt;ul&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;## New Features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;**Send Feedback**: Added feedback channel for users to report issues and suggestions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  - Menu bar: "Send Feedback..." menu item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  - Settings window: "Send Feedback" button at the bottom&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  - Auto-fills email with app version, macOS version, device model, and hardware UUID&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;**Quick Access Buttons**: Added "Send Feedback" and "Check for Updates" buttons at the bottom of the settings window for easy access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;## UI/UX Improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;**Menu Bar Alignment**: Fixed inconsistent left padding in menu bar dropdown (Settings item had extra indent compared to other items)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;**Single Key Picker Redesign**:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  - Changed background from gray to white, matching the combo key picker style&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  - Improved visual consistency between "组合键" and "单键" selectors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  - Updated dropdown icon to chevron.up.chevron.down for native macOS feel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;**Label Rename**: Changed "转录原文" to "转录结果" for clearer meaning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;## Technical Improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refactored SingleKeyPicker to use Menu with custom styled button for better control over appearance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Used clipShape for cleaner rounded corner rendering&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            </description><enclosure url="https://github.com/kyleqihua/voice-press-releases/releases/download/v0.0.21/VoicePress-0.0.21.dmg" sparkle:edSignature="yhPGOu4w4xbm2yn2o649Pu56Tjk6gHuGCt0sdtRMDehiHmXSKGo6GIC1zUF4vZBFwonvHQffn58PznsLvhX2AQ==" length="2993194" type="application/octet-stream" /></item><item><title>Version 0.0.22</title><pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 22:35:31 +0800</pubDate><sparkle:version>0.0.22</sparkle:version><sparkle:shortVersionString>0.0.22</sparkle:shortVersionString><description>
